dct_title_s: Cretaceous formation : including the green-sand marl beds (Sheet 1)
dct_description_sm: At head of title: Geological survey of New Jersey. Companion text is filed in RECAP. Call number 8565.672.01]. Shows railroads, roads, towns, etc. Includes 8 cross sections. Map cut in 2 sheets for encapsulation Companion text: Geology of New Jersey / G.H. Cook. 1868. Map is from companion atlas of 8 folded maps. [Book is filed in Lewis Annex B cage.Call number 8565.672.01].
dct_publisher_sm: [Newark, N.J.] : Geological Survey of New Jersey, 1868.
New York, N.Y. : New York Lithographic Engraving and Printing Company, 1866.
